        </div>

        <div class="col-md-4 col-xs-12">
          <div class="skill growth">
            <span class="icon-growth"></span>
            <h3>GROWTH SKILLS</h3>
            <p>Know number names and the count sequence; Count to tell the number of objects; Compare numbers</p>
            <div class="grey-box">
